{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc2e37c6a6","title":"七律·和周世钊同志","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"74c6c1a903","index":0,"year":1955,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"dc2e37c6a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"af46ce6af9","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，当时任湖南省教育厅副厅长兼湖南省立第一师范学校校长。"},{"id":"3630e72741","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尊前，尊同，酒杯。尊前，酒席前。"},{"id":"ebfa8044df","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"域外鸡虫事可衰，国际间的某些事件像鸡虫得失一样小，人们为这些小事而勾心斗角是可悲的。这里所指的具体内容待考。唐杜甫《缚鸡行》：“小奴缚鸡向市卖，鸡被缚急相喧争。家中庆鸡食虫蚁，不知鸡卖还遭烹。虫鸡于人何厚薄？吾比奴人解其缚。鸡虫得失无了时，注目寒江倚山阁。"},{"id":"645b496e4c","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"韶华，美好的年华，指人的青年时代。"},{"id":"8bd2fe0044","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赫暖台，在湖南省长沙市岳麓山岳麓书院。朱嘉曾称岳麓山顶为赫曦，后因称山上的台为赫曦台。清代因山上的台已毁，将原“赫曦台”匾额悬于岳麓书院“前台”，由此前台更名赫曦台。赫曦，光明盛大的样子。"}],"contents":[{"id":"01e9f5e01f","type":"title","text":"七律·和周世知同志","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6"},{"id":"af46ce6af9","type":"paragraph","text":"春江浩荡暂排何，又踏层峰望眼开。风起绿洲吹浪去，雨从青野上山来。尊前以谈笑人依旧，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6"},{"id":"3630e72741","type":"subtitle","text":"域外鸡虫事可衰。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6"},{"id":"ebfa8044df","type":"paragraph","text":"莫叹韶华问容易逝，州年仍到赫曦台回。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6"}],"page":{"id":"c01e92d203","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"dc2e37c6a6","start":45,"end":45}}}},"__N_SSG":true}